go-trafilatura — Apache-2.0
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Author:  markusmobius (Markus Mobius)
Source:  https://github.com/markusmobius/go-trafilatura

A faithful Go port of the Python original, used as the primary readable
reference for the core extraction algorithm.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
rs-trafilatura and web-page-classifier — MIT OR Apache-2.0
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Author:  Murrough Foley
Sources: https://github.com/Murrough-Foley/rs-trafilatura
         https://github.com/Murrough-Foley/web-page-classifier

rs-trafilatura is referenced for its page-type-aware architecture and
per-page-type extraction profiles; web-page-classifier is referenced for the
page-type feature set and classifier design. These projects are dual-licensed
MIT OR Apache-2.0; this port uses them under the Apache License, Version 2.0.

