WCXB — Web Content Extraction Benchmark dataset — CC-BY-4.0 (ATTRIBUTION REQUIRED)
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Author:  Murrough Foley
Dataset: https://huggingface.co/datasets/murrough-foley/web-content-extraction-benchmark
DOI:     10.5281/zenodo.19316874 (https://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.19316874)
License: Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 International (CC-BY-4.0)
         https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/

The WCXB dataset is used ONLY to train the page-type classifier model offline,
in the training/ project. Its CC-BY-4.0 license REQUIRES attribution, which this
notice provides.

The model.onnx shipped with this library is trained fresh from this public
dataset. It is NOT vendored or copied from rs-trafilatura's embedded model
binary.

